org.apache.nemo.compiler.frontend.spark.sql

Interface NemoSparkUserFacingClass

  • All Known Implementing Classes:
    DataFrameReader, Dataset, SparkSession

    public interface NemoSparkUserFacingClass
    Common interface for SparkSQL supporting Nemo classes containing the methods that are exposed to users. We currently support SparkSession, Dataset, DataFrameReader APIs.
